description: Welcome to 188 Athens Street! This sunny top-floor condo sits on a quiet one-way street and includes deeded parking directly outside the rear entrance. The ideal layout separates bedrooms from the open living/dining space—perfect for entertaining. Features include central AC, hardwood floors, a central vacuum system, and a Bose surround sound system. The updated kitchen offers granite counters, white cabinetry, marble tile backsplash, recessed lighting, and stainless steel appliances. The spacious primary bedroom has a bay window and 2 custom California Closets while the second bedroom works great as a guest room or office. Enjoy a private laundry room and a large private storage room in the basement. Just across from Foodie’s Market, 3 blocks to Broadway T, and minutes to the Seaport and the beach, you can’t beat this incredible West Broadway location!
